{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they took away, again, if they found anything left on us, they took it away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there already they were looking brutal, because there was one incident [SIGHING] where they kept-- there were Germans there already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, go fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And for some reason I, like, I got a little bit lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this Nazi he hit me with, like with a baseball bat on my-- on my back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he sort of knocked the wind out of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't breathe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my mother was behind me and she gave me a push.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I looked back and I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I-- I saw-- I saw-- I know I saw her face.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She was helpless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it's another sight which is very hard for me to--to forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so we were pushed along and we were taken out to the railroad station, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And over there there were wagons, cattle cars, waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they started to load them up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "As people came, they started to load up car number one, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And in every car where I went in there was like a couple of loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there was a pail of water-- fresh, I mean water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And one pail was like for sanitary purposes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we were jammed into that-- you-- you-- you people couldn't lay down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I want you to know that my great grandmother, my great grandmother, that I told you before, she was in the same transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "When she came to the ghetto the only thing she took along was her [NON-ENGLISH], because she made her own [NON-ENGLISH]-- her own [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And this is the only thing she held on to.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
